snippet.title: My Very First Published App: Meal Roulette
snippet.description:
Today, let's take a quick look at my very first application I released onto the Apple AppStore in August 2012.  This app is very raw and only contains a couple of features.  I'll go through a quick demo of what it does and talk about some of the difficulties of building something on a new platform for the very first time.

Enjoy.
